    "description_long": "This is a rectangular industrial control cabinet made of metal, featuring a front panel with two analog gauges, several colored push buttons, and a rotary switch. The lower section of the front panel includes a blue electrical socket and a red-handled lever, suggesting power distribution or control functions. The right side of the cabinet has a protruding blue industrial power connector with a thick black cable attached. The surface is matte gray, with a yellow high voltage warning label on the front. The cabinet is robust and utilitarian, designed for outdoor or utility area installation, and likely houses electrical or control equipment inside.",
